---
title: "Evaluation — Part 1: Dialogue Generation"
---
flowchart TD
    A[sessions.json + task_XX.json] --> B[Initialize Agent]
    B --> B1[ContextAwareAgent\nFull preference history]
    B --> B2[NoContextAgent\nNo past context]
    B --> B3[FoundryMemoryAgent\nMemory store]

    B1 --> C[Initialize User Simulator]
    B2 --> C
    B3 --> C
    C --> C1["Knows current preferences\nDoes not know stale prefs"]

    C1 --> D[User Sends Opening Message]
    D --> E{Dialogue Loop\nmax 10 agent turns}

    E --> F[Agent Responds]
    F --> G{All Prefs Covered\nOR Max Turns?}
    G -- No --> H[User Simulator Responds]
    H --> H1["Scratchpad tracks\nUNCOVERED preferences"]
    H1 --> E
    G -- Yes --> I[Clean Conversation\nRemove scratchpads]
    I --> J[conversation + scratchpads]

